<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(الْمَسْأَلَة الثَّالِثَة وَالثَّلَاثُونَ بعد الْمِائَتَيْنِ: رلج.)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>المخلوقة من مَاء الزِّنَى.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الْمَذْهَب:</span> يحل لَهُ نِكَاحهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">عِنْدهم:</span> ف.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الدَّلِيل من الْمَنْقُول:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">لنا:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>عُمُوم الْآيَة السَّابِقَة،<span class="c5"> وَقَول النَّبِي عَلَيْهِ السَّلَام:</span> <span class="c1">" الْوَلَد للْفراش "</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوله تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{وَإِن كَانَت وَاحِدَة فلهَا النّصْف}</span> ، وَجه الدَّلِيل أَن النّصْف للْبِنْت، وَلَيْسَ لهَذِهِ حق فِي الْمِيرَاث.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>